metadata.name: Uncharted Horizons
metadata.description:
"Uncharted Horizons" : A minimalist piece that captures the essence of a voyage into uncharted horizons. The artwork depicts a single boat on an endless sea, with nothing but the vastness of the horizon ahead. The minimalist approach emphasizes the limitless possibilities of what lies beyond.

Name: Uncharted Horizons
Artist: Shivayy
Collection Name: Surreal Worlds
Edition type: 1/1
Year: 2022
Dimensions: 2280x2280
